{"tid":2493843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人抄襲真係幾勁","createTime":"2021-04-18T08:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T08:21:09.000Z","uid":73407,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a661970f8e4222d6ff653a9122e7deb7fbf31599","tid":2493843,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:06:58.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post話馬雲好勁<br />\n有感而發<br />\n<br />\n中國所謂創科好多都係抄襲<br />\n只係中國保護主義<br />\n打壓封鎖外資企業<br />\n無競爭下先成功<br />\n<br />\n阿里抄amazon ebay<br />\n支付寶抄paypal<br />\n抄AWS整阿里雲 <br />\n抄Amazon GO搞無人商店<br />\n<br />\n騰訊QQ抄ICQ<br />\n百度抄google<br />\n微博抄twitter<br />\n優酷 土豆 愛奇藝抄youtube 同大量無版權片<br />\n人人網抄facebook<br />\n美團抄groupon<br />\n滴滴抄uber<br />\n無數唔同本業既公司都想抄Tesla<br />\n<br />\n直到兩年前大陸好多地方都仲用唔到mastercard visa （兩年無去唔知而家）<br />\n扶植銀聯<br />\n相反外國市場就任銀聯搶生意<br />\n<br />\n你話mewe抄facebook <br />\nfacebook抄myspace<br />\nsignal抄WhatsApp<br />\n佢地點抄都係係同業中競爭勝出<br />\n<br />\n中國同外國就帶住肥水不留別人田既鬥爭心態<br />\n係不對等地位有心抄襲再打壓<br />\n<br />\n中國人抄襲勁在抄完 再打壓你 再迫走你<br />\n仲有班好天真既人<br />\n覺得佢地有過人之處<br />\n<br />\n可能真係老左<br />\n班後生一出世就係抖音 微信 跑男 好聲音 淘寶 同愛國教育"},{"pid":"7543e616ed56678e54b43ad297ea5a0506b1aa6d","tid":2493843,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"世界是中國的"},{"pid":"949a4b5f517d8d9cfd0c54131d730cd34e1f14a5","tid":2493843,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:10:13.000Z","msg":"馬雲其實真係幾勁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2493611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2493611</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f928f7a68f7870a3e1a1087e660e4bc696ac600","tid":2493843,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"抄得好都唔係易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中国人連假雞蛋都做到就知佢哋好勁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0f499248107148feff164f475bc5fc55c37fd3","tid":2493843,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"美臀係抄？"},{"pid":"da4385faa71da19d6266b5cf1387482552462c1e","tid":2493843,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"有咩例子歡迎補充"},{"pid":"0ae7ed4a0eea754c5eb5f839372e2a3892a1f4fc","tid":2493843,"uid":187768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"QR code吹撚到自己發明咁"},{"pid":"c902f27db929f1dc3223d5d615b37b770c4988c7","tid":2493843,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e0f499248107148feff164f475bc5fc55c37fd3","tid":2493843,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"美臀係抄？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"叻 咁都畀你搵到一間無抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb498257f1e59a1823ff03b03daa04b0ef2496b6","tid":2493843,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"中國式創新代表人物<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh2gduD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh2gduD.jpg&h=ecf4ddbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ncm8O22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcm8O22.jpg&h=e06f87ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7URMPK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7URMPK.jpg&h=b240c114&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}